                                        <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530097.html" data-pid="278530097">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:291px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1A/wKgBEFpKWsqATMhGAAClJHwNR6w97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530097" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">大榛峪长城位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11319.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="怀柔" target="_blank">怀柔</a>渤海镇的北面、慕田峪长城以西、响水湖风景区的门口。大榛峪长城因交通不便，前来的游人稀少，至今仍保留着原始古朴的风貌。&nbsp;<br />
大榛峪长城属<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11319.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="怀柔" target="_blank">怀柔</a>境内的重边长城，从北沟的水关到响水湖内的磨石口关，全长约9公里，中间可分为三段：第一段是水关-西大楼—贾家口关，就是从三岔子村到姚校长的自留地；第二段是贾家口—牛犄边—驴鞍岭口；第三段是东边的旺泉峪—磨石口长城。长城的地势西高东低，最高点西大楼海拔986米。<br />
<br />
搞清路线图<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530100.html" data-pid="278530100">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:403px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1A/wKgBEFpKWsqAe2RWAADFNwSfKB459.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530100" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">蓝色的位置就是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11319.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="怀柔" target="_blank">怀柔</a>的大榛峪长城。透过这<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11386.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="张北" target="_blank">张北</a>京地区的明长城分布图可以看到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>地区可爬的野长城还是很多的，慢慢爬吧~~~<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530101.html" data-pid="278530101">
