            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">这是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11319.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="怀柔" target="_blank">怀柔</a>境内的长城分布，蓝色位置就是大榛峪长城。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530102.html" data-pid="278530102">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:405px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1B/wKgBEFpKWsuAK3psAAC6yX5wMlY03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530102" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">蓝色部分就是我们此次要徒步的长城：从牛犄边——驴鞍岭段。<br />
联系好农家院，出发<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530104.html" data-pid="278530104">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:753px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1C/wKgBEFpKWsuAfefdAAGiUvKvfcg39.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530104" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">我提前联系了大榛峪村三队的胡爱民农家院，他家就在长城脚下，我可以把车停在他家，爬完长城再在他家美美的吃上一顿。胡大哥的爱人王姐热情的给我们发了她家的位置。&nbsp;王姐电话、微信：13716308735<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530105.html" data-pid="278530105">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1C/wKgBEFpKWsuAU_2kAAC74Fq5Sqk24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530105" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">一路上远远的就能看到山上连绵不断的长城，感叹它的壮观，也让人对这次徒步充满期待。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530106.html" data-pid="278530106">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1D/wKgBEFpKWsyAUohLAAIfrfoqFtI35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530106" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530107.html" data-pid="278530107">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:633px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1D/wKgBEFpKWsyAbl0xAABh48TUd5I11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530107" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">大榛峪村就在响水湖景区入口处北侧，这里农家乐搞的火热，到处都可以看到农家乐的牌子，在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>各个郊区县中，农家乐搞的有特色有规模，值得去看看的，一数<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10042.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="平谷" target="_blank">平谷</a>的玻璃台，一数<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11319.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="怀柔" target="_blank">怀柔</a>的大榛峪。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530108.html" data-pid="278530108">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:916px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1D/wKgBEFpKWsyAVtSZAACHexqWk_M63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530108" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530109.html" data-pid="278530109">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:345px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1D/wKgBEFpKWs2AHaC6AAC3SQUhISU15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530109" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">大榛峪村有二队、三队，我们这次要去的是三队，红点处就是我们要停车的胡爱民农家院，红线部分就是我们要爬的长城。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530110.html" data-pid="278530110">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1E/wKgBEFpKWs2AYo_eAAGdSFlThRg25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530110" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530111.html" data-pid="278530111">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1E/wKgBEFpKWs2AVuBqAAD98O0Gd3Q91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530111" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">跟着导航的指引，进入大榛峪村三队，曲径通幽处就是胡爱民农家院，村子里貌似家家都挂着“农家院”的牌子，真是名副其实的农家乐旅游村。我们把车停在胡爱民家门口，王姐热情的招呼我们，并带我们去登城口。<br />
<br />
前往登城口<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530168.html" data-pid="278530168">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1E/wKgBEFpKWs6AY2g2AAHmXxTCr8I84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530168" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530114.html" data-pid="278530114">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1F/wKgBEFpKWs6AE0xdAAHxqJe1x3468.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530114" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">王大姐带着我们从村子里一路向北，几分钟之后到达登长城的路口，这个路口向左攀（向西）去往牛犄边方向，向右攀（向东）去往驴鞍岭方向。王姐说驴鞍岭方向陡，带着孩子有点危险。去牛犄边方向相对安全，这个方向也有2条路可走，一个是从下面就走长城，登烽火台，但是有一段路滑，她还是觉得带孩子不安全。另外一条路是走石头边墙，登烽火台，孩子走没问题。王姐身手矫捷的攀上了一个大<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/34881.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="高台" target="_blank">高台</a>，给我们指清了登城的石头路。还呼喊在一旁果园里干活的胡爱民大哥，告诉我们遇到任何问题都可以呼叫他，他会帮助我们。胡大哥曾经把一位摔伤的驴友从长城上背下山，虽然远远的我看不清胡大哥的长相，那也要给他一个大大的赞！<br />
<br />
走边墙&nbsp;直奔烽火台<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530116.html" data-pid="278530116">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/1F/wKgBEFpKWs6AffTEAAICLxSQTLs25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530116" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530117.html" data-pid="278530117">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/20/wKgBEFpKWs-AGNjIAARSii9Kal043.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530117" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530118.html" data-pid="278530118">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/20/wKgBEFpKWs-AX-TLAAM_izs1fBU04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530118" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530119.html" data-pid="278530119">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/20/wKgBEFpKWtCAH0ptAAMJr-8uLq429.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530119" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">这就是相对平缓的登烽火台的边墙，抬头可以望到前方的烽火台，回头可以望到出发的大榛峪村。虽然路不好走，碎石嶙峋，老二连走带爬的，但是没有风险，即使滑下去也有灌木挡着，没大事。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530120.html" data-pid="278530120">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/21/wKgBEFpKWtCAbsFXAAJOI0CdqGw40.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530120" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530121.html" data-pid="278530121">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/21/wKgBEFpKWtCAFfXDAAHtjWigT1070.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530121" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530122.html" data-pid="278530122">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/21/wKgBEFpKWtGADMy7AAImXMHt2EA43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530122" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530123.html" data-pid="278530123">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/21/wKgBEFpKWtGAeXw-AAKuhBeYAMc35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530123" />
