                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530133.html" data-pid="278530133">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/24/wKgBEFpKWtWAZa53AADXeyxE3X491.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530133" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">走长城会经过各式各样的烽火台，它们造就了每段长城独特的魅力，它们屹立在那里600多年，残破的身躯挡不住他顽强的风骨。每次徒步都会把登上一个个烽火台作为徒步目标，每次走进烽火台都会有控制不住的小激动。<br />
<br />
眺&nbsp;望<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530135.html" data-pid="278530135">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/25/wKgBEFpKWtWAEkTwAAHlBn1_pLw09.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530135" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530136.html" data-pid="278530136">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/25/wKgBEFpKWtWAOVbWAAEFFgBPnAs79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530136" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">在烽火台上向西望，可以看到山脊上“驴鞍岭”、“九眼楼”、“箭扣”、“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>结”、“天梯”、“鹰飞倒仰”……一路蜿蜒向西，我们在山上凝视远眺，感叹古人的智慧和毅力。<br />
<br />
野&nbsp;餐<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530138.html" data-pid="278530138">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/25/wKgBEFpKWtaAfNN6AAJH_LbSbqE41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530138" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530139.html" data-pid="278530139">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:337px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/26/wKgBEFpKWtaAI4ieAAHdR1ZW8yI69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530139" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">在烽火台的最上面就像是一个阳光大露台，看着长城，晒着太阳，吃野餐，真是惬意又拉风。<br />
<br />
<br />
继续攀登<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530141.html" data-pid="278530141">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/26/wKgBEFpKWtaAU-QvAAGsK9IvOHQ01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530141" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530143.html" data-pid="278530143">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/26/wKgBEFpKWteAIlF9AAE1BMGYfhc57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530143" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530145.html" data-pid="278530145">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/27/wKgBEFpKWteAEE3cAAG085NxsQc40.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530145" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">继续向西攀登，长城上貌似都是灌木，没有路，但是走的驴友多了，在靠近城墙边的一侧有一条能供一人通过的小路，我们排好队依次前行。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530146.html" data-pid="278530146">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/27/wKgBEFpKWteAC0sgAAGJcrSqcIo75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530146" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530147.html" data-pid="278530147">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/27/wKgBEFpKWtiAbnnmAAEg-2UL_1M76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530147" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530148.html" data-pid="278530148">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/27/wKgBEFpKWtiABH7hAAHtLMH07xA54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530148" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530149.html" data-pid="278530149">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/28/wKgBEFpKWtiAUjdRAAGpu_TI0kw85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530149" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">无论是多么残破的长城，都散发着无限的魅力，素颜、侧颜都上镜。<br />
<br />
眺望牛犄边<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530151.html" data-pid="278530151">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/28/wKgBEFpKWtmABTnQAANbVGcuAtQ32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530151" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">抬头仰望就是牛犄边，天为被、城为床，沐浴冬日暖阳。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530152.html" data-pid="278530152">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/29/wKgBEFpKWtmAJMjAAAOBEqsSKQM61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530152" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530153.html" data-pid="278530153">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/29/wKgBEFpKWtqAUJTxAALmKo2Ez4I34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530153" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530154.html" data-pid="278530154">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/29/wKgBEFpKWtqALjTDAAEBVhF2bQ859.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530154" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">前往牛犄边的城墙有一段塌方，考虑到孩子们的安全和时间，我们决定，在塌方路前不再前进，原路返回。不论走到那里，只要在长城上，就会被它的美所折服。<br />
<br />
原路返回<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530156.html" data-pid="278530156">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/2A/wKgBEFpKWtqAEV6GAAP_6fOVrRw02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530156" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530157.html" data-pid="278530157">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/2A/wKgBEFpKWtuACBLaAAHAuWvJwoY15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530157" />
