                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530163.html" data-pid="278530163">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/2E/wKgBEFpKWt6AKvRvAAPVS7k_Q7875.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530163" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530164.html" data-pid="278530164">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/2E/wKgBEFpKWt6AayL_AAQAi-l7Qbc85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530164" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">山上容易下山难，边墙这段石头路不仅非常崎岖，而且向下望是有点瘆得慌，老二遇到落差大的地方紧张的坐在地上往下蹭，我坚持不扶他，只在一米处看着他一点点往下走。冬天徒步的好处就是穿的厚，摔一跤也磕不破，裤子磨烂了也豁出去了，反正磨不到屁股。<br />
<br />
<br />
穿果园进村<br />
</p>
