            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">走完边墙的石头路，可以看到村路了，我们可以按上山时王姐带我们翻的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/34881.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="高台" target="_blank">高台</a>下去，但想想下去就危险，我们还是向右迂回走果园回村吧，也就200米的果园路。<br />
<br />
<br />
大榛峪村<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530171.html" data-pid="278530171">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/30/wKgBEFpKWuCAU49sAAGuxRpftfA55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530171" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530172.html" data-pid="278530172">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/30/wKgBEFpKWuCAMYEBAAIvgWYCOo854.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530172" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530173.html" data-pid="278530173">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/31/wKgBEFpKWuCAQ7qvAAGrtRQ0-R410.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530173" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530174.html" data-pid="278530174">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/31/wKgBEFpKWuGAFcjiAAEBJ8od3LU20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530174" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">回到大榛峪村，村里看不到太多人，夕阳笼罩下的小村庄格外安静祥和……我忍不住又回头仰望了身后的长城，四季轮回，长城一直默默的守卫着小村庄。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530175.html" data-pid="278530175">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:353px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/32/wKgBEFpKWuGAWfLRAADaxJOw1fM63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530175" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
农家院的晚餐<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530177.html" data-pid="278530177">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/32/wKgBEFpKWuGAfzRWAADbM-8ihJY45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530177" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530178.html" data-pid="278530178">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/33/wKgBEFpKWuGAL4X7AACM4m1cuPU52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530178" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530179.html" data-pid="278530179">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/33/wKgBEFpKWuKAYp_KAADLXUTBc9s17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530179" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530180.html" data-pid="278530180">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/34/wKgBEFpKWuKAYHNxAADYCtZNQdA91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530180" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530181.html" data-pid="278530181">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:447px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/34/wKgBEFpKWuKARCTuAACznV-GnfI45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530181" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">出发的时候王姐问我们想吃什么，现在冬天客人少，家里没备那么多食材，我们也不想给大姐添麻烦，说简单的做碗面就行。回来后看到王姐准备的手擀面还有自制的腊肠、凉菜，在这暖洋洋的房间吃上一碗手擀面，旅程圆满结束。&nbsp;<br />
此次徒步一共走了3公里，连走带玩历经4个小时，没有体能挑战，很轻松。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530182.html" data-pid="278530182">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:58px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/34/wKgBEFpKWuOAO6lpAABjoWJQgmE688.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530182" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8166790/278530183.html" data-pid="278530183">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:799px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FF/35/wKgBEFpKWuOAf1MXAAJxVEjqafU27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278530183" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">2017年｜冬<br />
我会带孩子们一站站的徒步长城，我相信体验是当下的，见识是积累的，影响是长久的……<br />
更多攻略欢迎关注“小尹博游”<br />
</p>
    
                        
